title: LED Blinker Notifications PrO v6.0.7 ApK
description:
LED Blinker Notification lets you to choose colors for notifications. its a very powerfull tool... 

Let LED Blinker Notifications (formerly LEDBlinker) show your missed calls, SMS, Facebook and Whatsapp messages. If you have no hardware led, the screen is used.
All apps are supported in the full version, click on the plus button on the top and add the missing.
This app is very simple to use and not much configuration is needed!
Tested with Xperia Z1 compact & Xperia Z
